{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Gabriella Morton</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The secret to Gabriella Morton's success is refined conceptualisation of an idea. Each artwork stands as evidence of her wrestling with the potential of scene, saying and shared experience. Klutch, Grant Shannon, Shalin and Norcal Guy have also recognized the immense future potential that Gabriella is hinting at.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"731\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-731x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-731x1024.jpeg 731w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-214x300.jpeg 214w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-768x1075.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-1097x1536.jpeg 1097w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-1463x2048.jpeg 1463w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-1320x1848.jpeg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-600x840.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/shades-of-you-scaled.jpeg 1829w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 731px) 100vw, 731px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Shades of You by Gabriella Morton</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Incubator</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Six 1 of 1 artworks comprise the Incubator series minted in December 2022. A reduced color palette to the merest essential of cinematic tones leaves the viewer to focus on the symbology. The lone figure holding the light, the disappearing couple, the cavernous depths, the hand that defies gravity and the mesmerised figure all convey more than what you see. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"712\" height=\"706\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/incubator.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/incubator.png 712w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/incubator-300x297.png 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/incubator-150x150.png 150w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/incubator-600x595.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/incubator-100x100.png 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 712px) 100vw, 712px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Incubator collection by Gabriella Morton</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Aperture</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>At the centre of Aperture is a glowing orange pupil and person. The stalagmites play the role of eyelashes and eye brows as the downward facing lens adds a pulling force into the abyss. Was fortunate to also pick up the photograph printed on metallic to enjoy beyond its tokenized global home. There is no better feeling than waking up to a 'gm' signed artwork everyday.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"562\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-300x225.jpg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-768x576.jpg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-400x300.jpg 400w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-1320x990.jpg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2025/01/aperture-gabriella-morton-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Aperture by Gabriella Morton collected by MintFace</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/gabriella-morton/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGabriella Morton | Line 133\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}